      "author": "github-actions[bot]",
      "description": "# Features\r\n- **Geocoding Search Bar**: A draggable search bar has been added to map views, which can be enabled in the settings. It supports finding locations via natural language search and by pasting coordinates in various formats.\r\n- **Map Context Menu**: Right-clicking on the map now opens a context menu with options to:\r\n    - Copy coordinates to the clipboard.\r\n    - Set the clicked location as the map's default center.\r\n    - Set the current zoom level as the default.\r\n    - Open the location in Google Maps.",
      "draft": false,
      "name": "1.1.1",
      "prerelease": false,
      "publishedAt": "2025-11-25T01:22:13Z",
      "tag": "1.1.1"
    },
