          "name": "styles.css",
          "size": 11875
        }
      ],
      "author": "github-actions[bot]",
      "description": "# Features\r\n- **Polygon support**: Points can now have a `polygon` property, which is rendered on the map. This includes a new `PolygonLayer`, data extraction logic for polygon coordinates, and a new \"Polygon points property\" setting.\r\n- **Local image backgrounds**: The map can now use a local image file as a background layer instead of a web-based tile server. This is configured via a new \"Image bounds\" setting.\r\n# UX\r\n- **Timeline View UX**: The timeline slider control is now draggable within the map container.\r\n- Autofit now triggers when it should.\r\n# Bugs\r\n- The map now correctly refreshes and re-renders when its window is moved.",
      "draft": false,
